## Quick Reference Commands

### Service Management
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `sudo systemctl status cloudflared` | Check status |
| `sudo systemctl restart cloudflared` | Restart service |
| `sudo journalctl -u cloudflared -f` | View logs |
| `sudo systemctl enable cloudflared` | Enable at boot |

### Updates
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `sudo apt-get update` | Update package list |
| `sudo apt-get upgrade cloudflared` | Upgrade cloudflared |
| `sudo systemctl restart cloudflared` | Restart after update |

### Health Checks
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `systemctl is-active cloudflared` | Running status |
| `cloudflared tunnel info ${TUNNEL_ID}` | Tunnel info (replace with tunnel ID) |
| `curl -I https://grafana.codeandcamera.me` | Test public access |

### LXC Operations (from Proxmox host)
| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `pct list` | List containers |
| `pct status ${CONTAINER_ID}` | Container status (replace with container ID) |
| `pct enter ${CONTAINER_ID}` | Enter container (replace with container ID) |
| `pct restart ${CONTAINER_ID}` | Restart container (replace with container ID) |
| `pct snapshot ${CONTAINER_ID} ${NAME}` | Create snapshot (replace with container ID and name) |

